                        <idno type="geonames" ref="https://www.geonames.org/8378691/ostia.html">Ostia</idno>
                    <p>The extent of emperor worship is significant at Ostia Antica. Epigraphic texts <ref target="#EmpWor000104.xml">EmpWor000104</ref> and <ref target="#EmpWor000105.xml">EmpWor000105</ref>
                        tell us that there was <ref target="monument-search#ostiaaedes">a temple (aedes) dedicated to Roma and Augustus in Ostia</ref>, which has subsequently been found archaeologically at the southern end of forum of Ostia.
                    </p>
